<s id='en97'>I 'll invest in early childhood education .</s>
<s id='vn97'>Tôi sẽ đầu tư vào giáo dục tuổi thơ .</s>
</spair>
<spair id='98'>
<s id='en98'>I 'll recruit an army of new teachers , and pay them higher salaries , and give them more support .</s>
